{"tid":1516723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用呢個方法收曬所有撐警藍尸皮","createTime":"2019-08-29T16:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T17:30:26.000Z","uid":236473,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"71a300a819ba8f9d81d395f7063c4a4d99c5a05f","tid":1516723,"uid":236473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:07:43.000Z","msg":"古乳有雲：「對付藍尸，就要比佢地更藍。」<br />\n<br />\n當你見到藍尸廢老係度撐警，大叫警察加油，你只需要回一句<br />\n「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">屌！d差佬用左兩個幾月都搞唔掂班廢青黃絲，真係哂嘥撚曬我地立稅人d錢！</span></span>」通常佢地開始思考人生。<br />\n<br />\n如果有腦少少就可能會話警察好好人，只會用最低武力，所以班廢青仲敢出黎。呢個時候你可以講：「咁咪姐係班差佬冇撚用囉。你睇下大陸d公安城管，一見到d破壞社會安寧既人就打9佢地，所以中國先咁安穩呀！」無論佢講咩都好，只要將個topic spin翻去差佬好撚廢就ok！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試諗下連藍尸廢老都覺得差佬好廢既時候，班警渣會有咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民分化藍尸廢老</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e84550a25981448c85b6678dc88655eb745b49","tid":1516723,"uid":236473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:08:11.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5c611a02172b807eb1418ce3ae2d8888c824ec73","tid":1516723,"uid":236473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:08:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化對家</span></span>"},{"pid":"a8be7d241b7395898a0f7cd2c3381142b1b7